16 (c) The Chief Executive Officer, as defined in section 2 of Chapter 21D of the General
17 Laws, shall work with the owning or managing party of eligible parking lots and garages
18 pursuant to subsection (a) for the purposes of carrying out subsection (a).
19 SECTION 2. This act shall take effect upon its passage.
